          th Name of Produce
          th Type of Produce
          th Date 
          th Time 
          th Tonnage (in metric tons)
          th Cost 
          th source of produce
          th Dealer Name
          th Branch Name
          th Contact
          th Price to be Sold At (per unit)
          th Action
